description: Step into modern living at Port 45, where style, comfort, and city energy converge. This bright two-bedroom, two-bath corner unit offers over 1,000 sq. ft. of thoughtfully designed space, including a versatile den ideal for a home office or creative retreat. Sunlight pours through floor-to-ceiling windows, highlighting an open layout that flows seamlessly from a sleek kitchen to living and dining areas made for entertaining. The southern-facing balcony adds extra space to relax, while the primary suite features a walk-in closet and spa-like bath with double vanity. Additional benefits include in-unit laundry and a deeded garage parking space. Residents enjoy a fitness center, club room, and a rooftop terrace with sweeping city and harbor views, along with concierge service, a pet-friendly community, and a dedicated pet spa. All this, in a prime location near the Seaport, Financial District, and South Boston’s best dining and nightlife.
